106
00:05:54,710 --> 00:05:59,480
J'imagine que l'hippopotame
a voulu charger...

107
00:05:59,520 --> 00:06:03,950
Le guide a pris son fusil
et a tiré, mais...

108
00:06:03,990 --> 00:06:06,960
